OL,3,CMother admits neglect following
OL,4,Calleged shaking death of toddler
OL,5,CCharlie Roberts
OL,7,FThe mother of a Darlington toddler who
OL,8,Fwas allegedly shaken to death by her
OL,9,Fpartner has changed her plea and
OL,10,Fadmitted neglect.
OL,12,FCharlie Roberts was one year and 10
OL,13,Fmonths old when he suffered a non-
OL,14,Fsurvivable head injury at his home.
OL,16,FAt the time, he was in the sole care
OL,17,Fof his mother's partner Christopher
OL,18,FStockton, 38, and he is is on trial at
OL,19,FTeesside Crown Court for murder and
OL,20,Fneglect, which he denies.
