OL,3,CMother admits neglect following
OL,4,Calleged shaking death of toddler
OL,5,CCharlie Roberts
OL,7,FCharlie's mother, Paula Roberts, 41,
OL,8,Fwas also on trial for neglect, having
OL,9,Fdenied the charge, but entered a
OL,10,Fguilty plea on Tuesday (3 December).
OL,12,FShe admitted failing to seek medical
OL,13,Fhelp for her little boy in December
OL,14,F2023 and January 2024 after he
OL,15,Fsuffered injuries to his private parts
OL,16,Fand to his ear.
OL,18,FJurors were told that Charlie suffered
OL,19,Fbruising in the months before his
OL,20,Fdeath.
