OL,5,CCharlie Roberts
OL,7,FThey were told Roberts installed a spy
OL,8,Fcamera above his cot and told her
OL,9,Fbrother in August that she hid it in a
OL,10,Fplant pot as she was concerned about
OL,11,FStockton.
OL,13,FShe was out having an eye test when
OL,14,FCharlie suffered fatal injuries on 12
OL,15,FJanuary.
OL,17,FThe prosecution said Stockton, who had
OL,18,Fstayed up late playing video games,
OL,19,Fcaused those injuries, which cause
OL,20,Fwidespread brain bleeding.
