OL,3,CMother admits neglect following
OL,4,Calleged shaking death of toddler
OL,5,CCharlie Roberts
OL,7,FHe made a 999 call in which he
OL,8,Frepeatedly said "come on mate" and
OL,9,F"wakey wakey" to the little boy, who
OL,10,Fwas not breathing.
OL,12,FThe call-handler talked him through
OL,13,Fhow to perform CPR and at one point
OL,14,FStockton, who was off work ill, said
OL,15,Fhe would pass out if he tried to count
OL,16,Fthe compressions he was doing on the
OL,17,Ftoddler.
