OL,3,CMother admits neglect following
OL,4,Calleged shaking death of toddler
OL,5,CCharlie Roberts
OL,7,FStockton was to tell paramedics,
OL,8,Fdoctors and the police that Charlie
OL,9,Fhad choked on a biscuit and that he
OL,10,Fpatted the child on the back and stuck
OL,11,Fhis fingers down the toddler's throat.
OL,13,FStockton said Charlie became "floppy"
OL,14,Fand so he called 999.
OL,16,FThe toddler died in hospital the next
OL,17,Fday.
OL,19,FStockton denies the charges of murder
OL,20,Fand neglect, and his trial continues.
